  <front>
   <head>Lirica latina - Lirica XLVIII</head>
  </front>
  <body>
   <lg xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="poem">
    <lg n="1">
     <l n="1">Haec vivens, nec certa satis natisque viroque,</l>
     <l n="2">si sua curae esset muta futura cinis,</l>
     <l n="3">illa, virum quamvis et natos semper amarit,</l>
     <l n="4">uxor quam magis et mater amare potest;</l>
     <l n="5">esset opes quamvis natis lictura viroque,</l>
     <l n="6">blanda licet natis, blanda viro fuerit;</l>
     <l n="7">haec, inquam, coniux Turini saxa paravit,</l>
     <l n="8">functa quibus voluit luce Labulla tegi.</l>
    </lg>
   </lg>
